statements: SELECT protein_id, protein_name, protein_sequence, molecular_weight, isoelectric_point FROM ProteinInfo;
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight, isoelectric_point, protein_id, protein_sequence FROM ProteinInfo;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInfo LIMIT 5;
SELECT protein_id, protein_name FROM ProteinInfo WHERE molecular_weight > 50;
SELECT protein_id, protein_name, isoelectric_point FROM ProteinInfo WHERE isoelectric_point < 7;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInfo WHERE molecular_weight > 100 AND isoelectric_point < 7.0 ORDER BY protein_name DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM ProteinInfo WHERE protein_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY molecular_weight ASC
SELECT protein_id, protein_name, protein_sequence FROM ProteinInfo WHERE molecular_weight BETWEEN 50 AND 150 AND isoelectric_point > 6.0
SELECT protein_id, protein_name, isoelectric_point FROM ProteinInfo WHERE protein_id = 2 OR protein_id = 4 ORDER BY protein_id
SELECT * FROM ProteinInfo WHERE protein_sequence LIKE '%GTAC%' OR protein_sequence LIKE '%AGTC%' ORDER BY protein_id
SELECT name, sequence FROM proteins WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE method = 'X-ray Crystallography';
SELECT id, name, molecular_weight FROM proteins;
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE result LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT id, name FROM proteins ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT name, sequence FROM proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 100
SELECT * FROM experiments WHERE method='X-ray crystallography' ORDER BY date DESC
SELECT id, name, sequence FROM proteins WHERE name LIKE 'A%' AND sequence REGEXP '^[A-Z]+$' LIMIT 5
SELECT experiment_id, method, result FROM experiments WHERE result IS NOT NULL AND date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT p.name, e.method, e.date FROM proteins p INNER JOIN experiments e ON p.id = e.protein_id WHERE e.result = 'Successful'
SELECT * FROM Proteins;
SELECT protein_name, protein_sequence FROM Proteins WHERE protein_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;

SELECT protein_name, experiment_name FROM Proteins JOIN Protein_Experiments ON Proteins.protein_id = Protein_Experiments.protein_id JOIN Experiments ON Protein_Experiments.experiment_id = Experiments.experiment_id;

SELECT protein_id, protein_name, protein_sequence FROM Proteins;
SELECT protein_name, protein_sequence FROM Proteins WHERE protein_id = 1;
SELECT protein_id, protein_name FROM Proteins WHERE protein_id > 5;
SELECT * FROM Experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT P.protein_name, E.experiment_name FROM Proteins P INNER JOIN Protein_Experiments PE ON P.protein_id = PE.protein_id INNER JOIN Experiments E ON PE.experiment_id = E.experiment_id;
SELECT * FROM Proteins;
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins ORDER BY molecular_weight DESC;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM Experiments WHERE researcher_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT peptide_sequence FROM Peptides WHERE protein_id = 2;
SELECT protein_name, gene_name FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 50000;
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 1000;
SELECT experiment_name, researcher_name FROM Experiments WHERE experiment_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT peptide_sequence FROM Peptides WHERE protein_id = 3 ORDER BY peptide_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM Measurements WHERE intensity > 5000 AND retention_time < 30 ORDER BY experiment_id, peptide_id;
SELECT protein_name, gene_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins JOIN Peptides ON Proteins.protein_id = Peptides.protein_id ORDER BY peptide_id;
SELECT * FROM proteins;
SELECT id, name FROM proteins WHERE id < 5;
SELECT sequence FROM proteins WHERE name = 'Protein1';
SELECT * FROM experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT name, sequence FROM experiments JOIN proteins ON experiments.protein_id = proteins.id;
SELECT * FROM proteins;
SELECT name, sequence FROM proteins WHERE id = 1;
SELECT annotations.annotation_id, peptides.sequence, proteins.name FROM annotations JOIN peptides ON annotations.peptide_id = peptides.peptide_id JOIN proteins ON peptides.protein_id = proteins.id;

SELECT experiments.experiment_id, proteins.name, measurements.intensity FROM experiments JOIN proteins ON experiments.protein_id = proteins.id JOIN measurements ON measurements.experiment_id = experiments.experiment_id;

SELECT peptides.peptide_id, proteins.name, annotations.function FROM peptides JOIN proteins ON peptides.protein_id = proteins.id JOIN annotations ON peptides.peptide_id = annotations.peptide_id ORDER BY peptides.peptide_id DESC;
